    "Feedback and Future Directions.",
    "All experts agreed that they would use RAGTAG to automate TS generation in their projects.",
    "Patty noted that \"It seems like a useful tool, and much better than writing test scenarios manually.",
    "They require minor adjustments but that is much easier than writing it from scratch.\"",
    "Gary further noted that \"As we noted, some of the scenarios were completely off."
